  "Description": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span>LOG CORRUPT <span class=\"name name-img\">CLOCK</span> RECOVERING DAMAGED SECTORS<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span><br><br><VAL_ON>\"captain found a ::: on the last walk out<br>says it'll bring us luck<br>we'll need it, cruise has been a ::: waste so far<br>all the asteroids just dust and ice<br>::: nonsense but better than nothing\"<>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span>日志损坏<span class=\"name name-img\">CLOCK</span>正在恢复损坏扇区<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span><br><br><VAL_ON>“船长在最后一次舱外行走时发现了一个:::<br>它说这个东西会给我们带来好运<br>我们的确需要好运，因为这趟巡航到目前为止可以说是在做:::无用功<br>所有的小行星不过是一些尘埃与冰块罢了<br>:::但是聊胜于无，总比没有好”<>",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span> 日誌毀損 <span class=\"name name-img\">CLOCK</span> 正在復原受損區塊 <span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span><br><br><VAL_ON>「船長上次在船外活動時找到了:::<br>說會帶來好運<br>我們會需要的，航程一直:::目前毫無成果<br>所有小行星都不過是塵埃和冰<br>:::胡說八道也比一無所獲好」<>"
  },
